message.entry: sqldbInternal must have string as a first argument
CheckJDBCServicesArgumentError expects at least 3 arguments, but got {0,number,integer}.

CheckJDBCServicesArgumentError expects only string arguments (4 arguments: path to jdbc driver, connection string, vector of strings, test string or 3 arguments: connection string, vector of strings, test string. If the path to the JDBC driver wasn't provided JDBC driver jar file should be in MATLAB javaclasspath).
